author: Brenda Goh
title: From filmmaker to medicine courier: volunteers helped Wuhan's virus fight
description: While most people in the Chinese city of Wuhan were hunkered down in their homes at the height of the country's coronavirus outbreak, Lin Wenhua was out on the empty streets in his car, driving toward the next person or task on his list.
